---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="JW Intimates | The Soulful Witness">
	<section class="space-y-12 py-20 animate-fade-in">
		<header class="space-y-4">
			<a href="/" class="text-slate-500 hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 mb-8">
				<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7" /></svg>
				Back Home
			</a>
			<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-7xl font-display animate-slide-up">
				The Soulful <span class="text-gradient">Witness</span>
			</h1>
			<p class="text-2xl text-slate-400 font-display animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
				JW Intimates: Holding space for the "Slow Exhale."
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
			<div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl space-y-4">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white font-display">Perspective & Integrity</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
					As a male photographer in an intimate space, my voice is rooted in professional transparency and respect. I am a witness, a guide, and a creative facilitator.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="glass p-8 rounded-3xl space-y-4">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white font-display">The "Slow Exhale"</h3>
				<p class="text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
					My goal is to provide a sanctuary where the armor can finally drop. It's about moving from performance to feeling; from hype to grounding.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="glass p-8 md:p-12 rounded-3xl space-y-8 text-slate-300 leading-relaxed animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white font-display">A New Vocabulary for Boudoir</h2>
			<p>
				We are shifting the narrative. We choose language that honors the sovereign body:
			</p>
			<ul class="space-y-4">
				<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<span class="text-blue-400 font-bold font-display">Sensual & Soul-stirring</span>
					<span class="text-slate-500">— not just "sexy". It's about how you feel, not just how you look.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<span class="text-blue-400 font-bold font-display">Grounding & Affirming</span>
					<span class="text-slate-500">— instead of "empowering". Hype is temporary; stability is permanent.</span>
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
					<span class="text-blue-400 font-bold font-display">Indulgence & Nourishment</span>
					<span class="text-slate-500">— luxury as a form of self-care, not elitism.</span>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-800 italic">
				"I see the weight my clients carry, and my goal is to provide a space where that armor can finally drop."
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="flex justify-center pt-8">
			<a href="https://jwintimates.com" class="btn-primary">Visit the Studio</a>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
